Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.34,0:01:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The attacks by the Gundams\Nsent by the Space Colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...reflected the colonies'\Nretaliatory intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ has masked its identity\Nin the Alliance Military...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Gundams' mission\Nis to attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ has finally taken\Ncenter stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With an army of elite soldiers\Nat his command...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...Treize Khushrenada plans to\Ndestroy the Alliance Military.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle between OZ and the\Nmobile suits sent to Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...causes serious repercussions\Non the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think your life's\Ntoo valuable for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-detonate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What would your parents think...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I said this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to live a good life\Nis to act on your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Take better care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Of your body, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Sylvia Noventa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in Marseilles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you wanna start there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The display of Leos, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been the main force\Nof the Alliance and OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was Romefeller so\Nset on using mobile suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people tend\Nto fear large machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the same time they\Nhave a strong admiration for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suits walk upright, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Foundation must've preferred\Na human looking battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...rather than one played out\Nwith buttons and switches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no difference when\Nit comes to killing men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If there were, it'd be as a game\Nthat toyed with people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:04:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In war, a frenzied death is\Nthe most honest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a few know that the\Nchaos caused by OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...is according to the\NRomefeller Foundation's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,An assembly of the Romefeller\NFoundation and invited guests...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...was being held on the\Noutskirts of Bremen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Romefeller Foundation was\Nformed from European royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With their enormous financial\Npower and connections...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...the aristocrats poured their\Nenergy into weapons development.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They provided mobile suits\Nto the Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...and became powerful enough to\Npull off the latest coup d'etat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't blame you, considering\Nwhat I did last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that door are people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...responsible for the death of\Nyour father and Sanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But today you mustn't\Ndo anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to act appropriately\Nfor a sovereign...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the peace-oriented\NSanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, the United Earth\NSphere Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...requested considerable funds\Nand assistance for world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't hesitate to cooperate\Nwith them for world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Alliance started seeking\Npeace through dialogue alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth has too many disputes that\Ndialogue alone can't settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't a system of control what\Nhumanity truly needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely how control\Nwill be exercised now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how peace\Ncan be maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance lacked the\Nnecessary talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Many responsibilities are\Nrequired to rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But they attempted to run away\Nfrom those responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the traditions\Nneeded to rule an era.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The world was corrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...with imperfect ideas\Nlike equality and freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The time's arrived where we\Nmust once again take control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe OZ's using these\Nmethods to take over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Romefeller Foundation\Nkept such ideas to itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...while hiding its presence and\Nagendas within the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ took advantage\Nof the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...saying they'd achieve world\Npeace, if the Alliance couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So the war will continue, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ must keep winning in\Norder to continue ruling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The rewards of victory and\NOZ's success go hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ's dissolution of former\Npolicies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...was a revolution against the\Nsystem's misrule and poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The nations in the\NRomefeller Foundation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...will want to take part only\Nin wars they're certain to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So OZ needs the strongest mobile\Nsuit troops in order to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Gundams can defeat OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ sees the Gundams\Nas a serious menace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By threatening to directly\Nattack the colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...OZ completely silenced\Nthe Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Romefeller Foundation is\Ntrying to destroy the Gundams...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...as soon as they're able.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll sacrifice lives\Nin order to gain rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But Heero sacrificed\Nhis own life to save others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to introduce you to\Nthe conqueror of the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This gentleman is a brave\Nknight fighting for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...in his endless quest\Nto attain world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A member of Romefeller\Nand OZ's chief commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize Khushrenada!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Some think OZ's military power\Nand mobile suit forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...may result in excess rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rule" is commonly associated\Nwith oppression and arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a way to keep\Nambitions under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,God let humanity run free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So what humanity needs is\Na system over and above God's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,God couldn't have predicted this\Nworld with never-ending wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure God would understand\Nthe steps we're taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,These people see wars through\Nrose-colored glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing we say will change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena? Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all very mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Gundams will come\Nto rectify your mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of those who're\Ntrampled by this whitewash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking to them is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lieutenant\NLucrezia Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies, Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me; she's the younger\Nsister of a friend I invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth was she\Ntrying to get at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She must've sensed our\Nanxiety toward the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's saying "be confident".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the Gundams, I want\Na word about Zechs Merquise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know his skills, but you're\Ngiving him too much freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he's rebuilding the\Nself-detonated Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...in Lake Victoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's insane to be fixing\Nthe mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...that we considered a menace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That Gundam should be destroyed\Nas a warning to the colonies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Foundation decides to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll tell Colonel Zechs\Nto destroy the Gundam at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that rumors about\Nthe Gundams were so widespread.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It shows the significance of the{\i0}\N{\i1}damage they've rendered to OZ.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His Excellency didn't seem{\i0}\N{\i1}to agree, though...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't help it, if they're\Norders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you follow orders{\i0}\N{\i1}and destroy the Gundam?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a ball of energy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's hard to escort her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How much does she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems that Mr. Darlian,{\i0}\N{\i1}her foster father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...told her a lot before{\i0}\N{\i1}he passed away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told her you're a respectable{\i0}\N{\i1}and trustworthy soldier...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...who was brought up{\i0}\N{\i1}in Sanc Kingdom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I also said you alone were there{\i0}\N{\i1}when Gundam Zero One self-detonated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that you're reconstructing{\i0}\N{\i1}the Gundam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which makes Relena believe{\i0}\N{\i1}that the Gundam pilot...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Heero Yuy, must've{\i0}\N{\i1}somehow lived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero Yuy... so that's\Nthe pilot's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relena has some connection{\i0}\N{\i1}with him, much like yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the update, Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wouldn't you tell{\i0}\N{\i1}her about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over and out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Zechs Merquise,\Nfrom the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...responsible for this\Nblood bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I could set fire to this castle\Nand burn it down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But God would never forgive\Nme if I did such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll be punished\Nfor my profanity toward God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then an appropriate\Npunishment must be planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God's merely an imaginary\Nfigure created by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Marshal Noventa of the United Earth\NSphere Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...objected to armament\Nexpansion, to deter rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed a request for arms\Nreduction and disarmament...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the Earth's nations\Nand the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But his untimely death\Nput an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ chose that day as\Nthe dawn of a new era...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and tricked the Gundams into\Nshooting down Noventa's shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let it obstruct\Nour peace proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Marshal!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rash now, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result of this tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...the road to peace may\Nhave been lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You must escape at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your concern,\NCaptain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Many soldiers from the United\NEarth Sphere Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...are still here in Marseilles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ will probably carry out\Nplans to attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the city\Ncould be protected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...because the Alliance\Nhas a base here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But now the base poses the\Ngreatest threat toward the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But leaving my memories\Nof life with my grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...has taken longer\Nthan I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Marshal Noventa was\Na fine person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He always thought about how\Nto help achieve world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather's no longer here,\Nbut his heart still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll live my life remembering\Nthat he's here in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it OZ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Ten Aries suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They think they can capture this\Nplace with 10 mobile suits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we won't\Ngive up that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get yourself to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the Aries from residential\Nareas, and commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Leos, return fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like a guerrilla attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll destroy all those Leos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What've I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Alliance's Leos are retreating{\i0}\N{\i1}to the underground channels!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Probably they're the main forces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All Aries, assemble at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The underground channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty obvious decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd get in your way\Nwith this arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let OZ find out\Nwe've got a Gundam in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's just a few of us left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are we doomed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry to point 211{\i0}\N{\i1}of the channels!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylvia Noventa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aries suits have entered\Nthe channels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No choice but to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Commander!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a Gundam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's it doing here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Aries are only a block away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop retreating and\Nfire as they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Commander?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Probably can't buy much time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but we'll resist until{\i0}\N{\i1}the pilot returns.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll manage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are we protecting the Gundam?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah; it'll be our backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Continue fire!{\i0}\N{\i1}Don't ease up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you, Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All Leos in the channels{\i0}\N{\i1}are destroyed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're heading out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a Gundam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why's it here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get rid of you before\Nthe others catch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get involved in a battle\Nbetween OZ and the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't afford to have\Nanyone see the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Aries suits destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a miracle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could this unidentified\Nmobile suit be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever it is, I'm\Nextremely grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You said your name\Nwas Heero Yuy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero Yuy, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my grandfather's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who killed\NMarshal Noventa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I accidentally shot down\NMarshal Noventa's shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing him and other people\Nwho'd advocated peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only thing I can\Ndo for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylvia Noventa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't undo my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the anger felt by\Nthe Marshal's loved ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the regrets of\Nthe Marshal's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...can be somewhat eased\Nif you pull that trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You obviously just wanna\Ntake the easy way out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only answer\NI can offer you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand that I didn't\Ncome here to make you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pay a visit\Nto your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard she's in Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where it starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes to every family member,\Nseeking their verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything he does is thorough\Nand well thought out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything Heero Yuy does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wars are nothing but\Nrepulsive killings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so\Nclear-cut about it all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way I can live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam Zero One has been destroyed\Nas per orders, Inspector Acht.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But would you object if\NI collected the remains?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not satisfied with the\Ndocuments we submitted?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather confirm the remains\Nwith my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I need to prepare\Na document of my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...to satisfy the hard-liners\Nof the Romefeller Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't imagine I'll find\Nanything out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs Merquise isn't likely\Nto be careless with details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't any Gundam parts\Nleft at the Lake Victoria base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs is fond of mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see him changing his\Nways for a request from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What will he gain by opposing\Nthe Romefeller Foundation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Romefeller's taking\Nover this era.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To move into the top ranks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...we just need to prove Zechs\Nbetrayed his official orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inspector is just trying\Nto find faults with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...so he can score some points\Nwith the Romefeller Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't find anything different\Nfrom the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I had to involve you\Nin my little performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it'd be a real waste\Nto destroy the Gundam Zero One...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...at this point in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've destroyed most of\Nthe Tallgeese's spare parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case I'll just have\Nto be more careful with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No pilot can harm the\NTallgeese and Colonel Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true. There is at least\None man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A war is supposed to\Nbe heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But Heero places his own destiny\Nin the hands of Mrs. Noventa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs longs for a decisive\Nbattle as a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Noin invites Heero to Antarctica\Nwhere Zechs awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Acht pursues them\Nwith his own forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam revival is about\Nto ignite its own new blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 15,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"To the Battleground, Antarctica".
